'''Office Sway'''是一款[[Microsoft_Office|Microsoft Office]]家族的[[演示程序|演示程序]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://blogs.office.com/2014/10/01/announcing-office-sway-reimagine-ideas-come-life/|title = Announcing Office Sway: reimagine how your ideas come to life|date = 2014-10-01|accessdate = 2014-10-01|website = Office Blogs|publisher = [[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|last = |first = |archive-date = 2014-10-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141001165034/http://blogs.office.com/2014/10/01/announcing-office-sway-reimagine-ideas-come-life/|dead-url = no}}</ref>  Sway允許用戶組合文本和媒體建立一個可演示的網页。用戶可以使用從本地裝置上傳内容，或從互聯網獲取資源，例如[[Bing|Bing]]、[[OneDrive|OneDrive]]、[[YouTube|YouTube]]、[[Google|Google]]和[[Facebook|Facebook]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.engadget.com/2014/10/01/microsoft-sway/|title = Microsoft's Sway lets you share ideas on the web without any design skills|date = 2014-10-01|accessdate = 2014-10-01|website = [[Engadget|Engadget]]|publisher = [[AOL|AOL]]|last = Finga|first = John|archive-date = 2014-10-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141002131421/http://www.engadget.com/2014/10/01/microsoft-sway/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

Sway文档存储在微软的服务器上，和[[微软账户|微软账户]]绑定，可以通过任意[[瀏覽器|瀏覽器]]使用[[Office_Online|Office Online]]網頁應用查看或編輯，也可以使用[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]和[[iOS|iOS]]版應用（目前正在開發針對Android和Windows Phone的應用程序）。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.winbeta.org/news/sway-coming-windows-10-available-more-countries-ipad-iphone|title = Sway coming to Windows 10, now on iPad, available in more countries on iPhone|last = Brengel|first = Kellogg|date = 2015-06-25|work = |access-date = |via = |publisher = WinBeta|archive-date = 2015-06-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150627235533/http://www.winbeta.org/news/sway-coming-windows-10-available-more-countries-ipad-iphone|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://blogs.wsj.com/personal-technology/2014/10/01/microsoft-sway-aims-to-automate-beautiful-responsive-web-design/|title = Microsoft Sway Aims to Automate Beautiful, Responsive Web Design|date = 2014-10-01|accessdate = 2014-10-01|website = [[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|publisher = [[Dow_Jones_&_Company|Dow Jones & Company]]|last = Olivarez-Giles|first = Nathan|archive-date = 2014-10-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141001151942/http://blogs.wsj.com/personal-technology/2014/10/01/microsoft-sway-aims-to-automate-beautiful-responsive-web-design/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 開發歷史 ==
在2014年10月1日，微軟發佈Sway的邀請預覽版本。2015年6月6日公开发布，它不需要[[Office_365|Office 365]]訂閱。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://money.cnn.com/2014/10/01/technology/microsoft-sway/index.html|title = Meet Sway, Microsoft's first new Office app in a decade|date = 2014-10-01|accessdate = 2014-10-01|website = [[CNN_Money|CNN Money]]|publisher = [[Time_Warner|Time Warner]]|last = O'Toole|first = James|archive-date = 2014-10-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141005054426/http://money.cnn.com/2014/10/01/technology/microsoft-sway/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>iOS應用最早于2014年10月31日新西蘭地區發布預覽版。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url = http://blogs.office.com/2014/11/17/touching-base-sway-preview/|title = Touching base on Sway Preview|date = 2014-11-17|accessdate = 2014-11-17|website = Office Blogs|publisher = [[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|last = |first = |archive-date = 2014-11-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141120063648/http://blogs.office.com/2014/11/17/touching-base-sway-preview/|dead-url = no}}</ref>在2015年1月28日，Sway開始允許用戶從某些服務嵌入代碼，如[[SoundCloud|SoundCloud]]和[[Vine|Vine]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://blogs.office.com/2015/01/28/sway-feature-updates-internet-embeds-and-more/|title = Sway feature updates—Internet embeds and more!|date = 2015-01-28|accessdate = |website = Office Blog|publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2015-09-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930183153/https://blogs.office.com/2015/01/28/sway-feature-updates-internet-embeds-and-more/|dead-url = no}}</ref>{{Infobox software|name = Sway for Windows|released = {{release date and age|2015|8|2}}|latest release version = 17.6103.20331.0|latest release date = 2015年8月6日|size = 62.2 MB|website = [https://www.microsoft.com/zh-cn/store/apps/sway/9wzdncrd2g0j Windows Store]}}{{Infobox software|name = Sway for iOS|released = {{release date and age|2015|1|8}}|latest release version = 1.5|latest release date =2015年8月5日|size = 20.8 MB|language = 英語，荷蘭語，法語，德語，意大利語，日語，葡萄牙語，西班牙語|website = [https://itunes.apple.com/n